---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Speaking - David Henzel"
  description="Book David Henzel to speak at your event. Topics include conscious leadership, the Love Not Fear operating system, AI + entrepreneurship, and self-leadership systems."
>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="pt-16">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-4">
      Speaking
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-5">
      I speak about conscious leadership, building companies from a place of love, and the systems that help people find their purpose. Whether it's a keynote, workshop, webinar, podcast, or university lecture, I bring real stories from 25+ years of building.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      Interested? Email me: <a href="mailto:dh@davidhenzel.com?subject=Speaking%20Inquiry" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-3 decoration-border hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent transition-colors">dh@davidhenzel.com</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-t border-border my-12" />

  <!-- Talk Topics -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary/60 mb-8">Talk Topics</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Love Not Fear: The Operating System for Conscious Leadership</p>
        <p>How to make better decisions by understanding the two forces that drive every choice, and building systems that keep you operating from love.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">From Introvert to CEO: Building Companies from a Place of Love</p>
        <p>The personal story of a self-described recovering introvert who built and sold multiple companies, and how self-awareness became his greatest competitive advantage.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">AI + Entrepreneurship: Building the Future Without Losing Your Soul</p>
        <p>How AI is reshaping entrepreneurship, and why the founders who will win are the ones who stay human-centered in an increasingly automated world.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Self-Leadership Systems: Purpose, Values, Vision, Habits</p>
        <p>A practical framework for getting clear on who you are, what you want, and how to build daily systems that move you toward it. The four pillars of the LNF operating system.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">For Universities: Helping Students Find Their Path</p>
        <p>Helping students and young people figure out what they really want to do with their life, what to study, and how to build a foundation of self-awareness before the world tells them who to be.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground mb-1">Love Not Fear Workshops: Interactive Team Sessions</p>
        <p>Half-day or full-day workshops for teams and organizations. Participants discover their purpose, define their values, and build personal operating systems. Creating alignment from the inside out.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-t border-border my-12" />

  <!-- Past Appearances -->
  <section>
    <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary/60 mb-6">Past Appearances</h2>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Keynotes, panels, and podcasts on entrepreneurship, conscious leadership, and self-leadership systems.
    </p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed list-none">
      <li>Entrepreneurs' Organization (EO), Member & Speaker</li>
      <li>Forbes Business Council, Guest Contributor</li>
      <li>Entrepreneur on Fire Podcast</li>
      <li>Marketing Speak Podcast by Stephan Spencer</li>
      <li>Radical Responsibility Podcast with Fleet Maull</li>
      <li>Org Design Podcast</li>
      <li>The Startup Chat Podcast, Multiple Appearances</li>
      <li>Running Remote, Future of Distributed Teams</li>
      <li>SaaStock, Building Companies with Purpose</li>
      <li>SEED Slovenia</li>
      <li>University guest lectures, Self-Leadership for Students</li>
      <li>Corporate workshops & webinars, Love Not Fear for Teams</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <hr class="border-t border-border my-12" />

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-2">
      I'm available for keynotes, workshops, webinars, podcasts, and university lectures.
    </p>
    <p class="text-base text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      Email me: <a href="mailto:dh@davidhenzel.com?subject=Speaking%20Inquiry" class="text-foreground underline underline-offset-3 decoration-border hover:text-accent hover:decoration-accent transition-colors">dh@davidhenzel.com</a>
    </p>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
